## Design Philosophy

* Python is the UI language
* Minimal API surface
* Predictable behavior
* No hidden magic
* Framework-managed CSS & JS

PyUI focuses on **clarity, simplicity, and developer productivity**.



## Project Status

* Stable core
* Actively developed
* API may evolve
* Open to contributions



